Text: This is my first upload. Hopefully it works. If not, let me know and I will try again.

Once you have seeded it fully, and you can see other people are seeding (the number of seeders is above 1) then you can shut down and travel without an issue, as other people can seed the file for you (they have 100% of it and are sharing it back).
